_sText:
This is a CS:S port of KULCS from INTERLOPER - D, the Half-Life 2 workshop map, which can be found here

The map has been completely unedited, aside from an easier entrance into bombsite A for CT's, and the sv_cheats trigger being removed from the trainstation entrance. Keep in mind that THIS MAP WAS NOT MEANT TO BE PLAYED IN CS:S. IT'S BEEN MADE PURELY FOR FUN!

I DID NOT MAKE THIS, FULL CREDIT GOES TO CaptainBleysFire !!!!

Enjoy this absolute mess of a map! :D
